      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "You're the one that got me Dr. #p512#'s #t4031071#, right? Good to see you. You didn't forget my plea for help down the road. I've been busily working on the fossils these days. Can you help me out by any chance?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Thank you. I've been busily investigating the leaf fossils of a plant, but this is much tougher than I thought. The leaves that are shown on this fossil are very uniquely formed..."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "I need samples that I can compare with in detail. You'll find various plants all around Ellinia. I need you to gather up a few of those, #b20 #t4031072#s#k to be exact. I'll be waiting for you. Please hurry!"
        },
        "2": {
          "_dirName": "2",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "The plants that can be used for samples are usually bigger than other plants. They usually grow in the northern forest of #m10002000#. You'll be able to find it in no time."
        }
      },
